text: KPIK-LP (96.5 FM) is a low-power radio station licensed to Stayton, Oregon, United States. The station is currently owned by Santiam Community Radio Corporation. ==References== ==External links== * PIK-LP PIK-LP Category:Marion County, Oregon Category:Stayton, Oregon Category:Radio stations established in 2003 Category:2003 establishments in Oregon
